agreement_id=AsoQuoteHeadersAll.CONTRACT_ID)AgrimentName, (select source_name from jtf_rs_resource_extns where resource_id =AsoQuoteHeadersAll.resource_id)SalesRepresentative, (select full_name from hca, apps.hz_parties hp, apps.hz_contact_points hcp WHERE hca.party_id = hp.party_id AND hp.party_id = hcp.owner_table_id AND hcp.owner_table_name = 'HZ_PARTIES' AND hp.party_id = = hza.cust_account_id --AND and hzps.party_site_id = hzas.party_site_id AND hzl.location_id = hzps.location_id AND hzsu.site_use_code = 'BILL_TO' AND hzsu.PRIMARY_FLAG='Y' AND hzsu.ORG_ID=AsoQuoteHeadersAll.org_id AND hzsu.cust_acct_site_id = hzas.cust_acct_site_id AND hzsu.org_id = hzas.org_id) caddr1, (SELECT DECODE(hzl.address2, NULL, NULL, ', '||hzl.address2)||', '||hzl.city||', '||hzl.country||', '||hzl.postal_code LOCATION FROM hz_parties hzp, hz_cust_accounts hza, hz_cust_acct_sites_all hzas, hz_cust_site_uses_all hzsu, hz_party_sites hzps, hz_locations hzl WHERE hzp.party_id = AsoQuoteHeadersAll.party_id and hza.party_id = hzp.party_id AND hzas.cust_account_id = hza.cust_account_id --AND and hzps.party_site_id = hzas.party_site_id AND hzl.location_id = hzps.location_id AND hzsu.site_use_code = 'BILL_TO' AND hzsu.PRIMARY_FLAG='Y' AND hzsu.ORG_ID=AsoQuoteHeadersAll.org_id AND hzsu.cust_acct_site_id = hzas.cust_acct_site_id AND hzsu.org_id = hzas.org_id) caddr2, (select DISTINCT jreb.source_name AS resource_name from jtf_rs_resource_extns jreb, (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER from per_phones where phone_type='WF') pp, (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER from per_phones where phone_type='W1') ppfax where jreb.source_id = pp.parent_id(+) and jreb.resource_id=AsoQuoteHeadersAll.resource_id and jreb.source_id = ppfax.parent_id(+)) srespo , (select DISTINCT jreb.source_phone from jtf_rs_resource_extns jreb, (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER from per_phones where phone_type='WF') pp, (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER from per_phones where phone_type='W1') ppfax where jreb.source_id = pp.parent_id(+) and jreb.resource_id=AsoQuoteHeadersAll.resource_id and jreb.source_id = ppfax.parent_id(+)) sphone, (select DISTINCT jreb.source_email from jtf_rs_resource_extns jreb, (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER from per_phones where phone_type='WF') pp, (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER from per_phones where phone_type='W1') ppfax where jreb.source_id = pp.parent_id(+) and jreb.resource_id=AsoQuoteHeadersAll.resource_id and jreb.source_id = ppfax.parent_id(+)) semail, (select pp.PHONE_NUMBER from (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER ,DATE_FROM,DATE_TO from per_phones where phone_type='W1') pp, per_all_people_f ppf , (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER,DATE_FROM,DATE_TO from per_phones where phone_type='WF') ppfax where TRUNC (SYSDATE) BETWEEN ppf.effective_start_date AND ppf.effective_end_date and ppf.person_id=pp.parent_id(+) AND ppf.person_id = TO_NUMBER(AsoQuoteHeadersAll.ATTRIBUTE10) and ppf.person_id=ppfax.parent_id(+) and TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN TRUNC(pp.DATE_FROM) AND NVL(pp.DATE_TO,SYSDATE+1)) csrphone, (select ppf.EMAIL_ADDRESS from (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER ,DATE_FROM,DATE_TO from per_phones where phone_type='W1') pp, per_all_people_f ppf , (select parent_id,PHONE_NUMBER,DATE_FROM,DATE_TO from per_phones where phone_type='WF') ppfax where TRUNC (SYSDATE) BETWEEN ppf.effective_start_date AND ppf.effective_end_date and ppf.person_id=pp.parent_id(+) AND ppf.person_id = TO_NUMBER(AsoQuoteHeadersAll.ATTRIBUTE10) and ppf.person_id=ppfax.parent_id(+) and TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN TRUNC(pp.DATE_FROM) AND NVL(pp.DATE_TO,SYSDATE+1)) csremail, (SELECT qsvl.Meaning from ASO_QUOTE_STATUSES_VL qsvl where qsvl.QUOTE_STATUS_ID=AsoQuoteHeadersAll.QUOTE_STATUS_ID) status FROM ASO_QUOTE_HEADERS_ALL AsoQuoteHeadersAll where AsoQuoteHeadersAll.quote_number =:pquoteno --67968 and quote_version in (select max(quote_version) from ASO_QUOTE_HEADERS_ALL where quote_number =:pquoteno )
